author: Joe Scott
description:
Compare news coverage. Spot media bias. Avoid algorithms. Try Ground News today and get 40% off your subscription by going to  https://ground.news/joescott

Clone Robotics’ new prototype (named Protoclone) uses hydraulic muscles that work much more like the human body. More efficient perhaps, but there’s not getting around it - they’re creepy as hell.

Today we’re talking about Clone Robotics, plus updates on life extension research, AI therapists, and how to stand out in the age of AI slop.
